# README
Data Science @ William & Mary.

This website is built using R's rmarkdown package.
A convenience script (build.R) is provided in the repo.
To create the site, simply run:

    ```
    Rscript build.R
    ```

from the commnand line.

Requires the rmarkdown package.

The site layout and organization are defined in the YAML file (_site.yml) and cascading style sheet (styles.css).
